y were engineered to conserve mountain soil, reduce erosion, and capture rainwater. **media[2731936,2731939]** Their fertility provides ideal conditions for cultivating many of Jazan's signature crops, including Saudi coffee, corn, millet, sesame, and aromatic plants, all of which thrive in the region's temperate climate and rich mountain soil.Beyond their agricultural role, the terraces are a living cultural and architectural heritage that reflects centuries of traditional farming knowledge. **media[2731933,2731935]** Resembling vast green staircases climbing toward the peaks during the rainy season, the terraces create one of the region's most distinctive natural views. As Jazan continues to expand its agricultural and tourism sectors, these remarkable landscapes have become a major attraction, offering visitors breathtaking mountain views, a glimpse into age-old farming practices, and an authentic experience of the region's rural heritage. **media[2731940]**", "content": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PAID PLANS", "keywords": ["jazan", "mountains", "nature", "sustainability", "farming", "agriculture", "harvesting", "saudi arabia"], "creator": ["saudi gazette"], "language": "english", "country": ["saudi arabia"], "category": ["lifestyle", "top"], "datatype": "news", "pubDate": "2026-07-04 12:10:31", "pubDateTZ": "UTC", "fetched_at": "2026-07-04 12:14:12", "image_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa/saudigazette/uploads/images/2026/07/04/2731937.webp", "video_url": null, "source_id": "saudigazette", "source_name": "Saudi Gazette", "source_priority": 356263, "source_url": "https://saudigazette.com.sa", "source_icon": "https://n.bytvi.com/saudigazette.png", "sentiment": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "sentiment_stats": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_tag": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN PROFESSIONAL AND CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_region": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_org": "ONLY AVAILABLE IN CORPORATE PLANS", "ai_summary": "ONLY AVAILABL